msgid ""
"Optional field representing the platform for :manual:`generators <cmake-"
"generators(7)>` that support it."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/presets/configurePresets-properties.rst:94
msgid "See :option:`cmake -A` for possible values."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../manual/presets/configurePresets-properties.rst:96
msgid ""
"``architecture`` may be either a string or an object with the following "
"fields:"
